---
layout: landing-layout.njk
title: ""
description: "HomeStart — early access. See the full cash you’ll need to buy, track savings, test affordability, and plan with clarity. Not a lender. Join the waitlist."
---

{% from "icons-features.njk" import icon %}

<header class="site-header" id="site-header" data-header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    {% include "brand-logo.njk" %}
    <nav aria-label="Primary">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#showcase">Preview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#waitlist" class="nav-cta">Join waitlist</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="main">
  <section class="hero-shell" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="section hero">
      <div class="hero-main">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="hero-eyebrow">Early access · iOS in development</p>
          <h1 id="hero-heading">Know your real cash to buy a home.</h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">See the full cash you’ll need to buy—not just the down payment. Track savings against it, test what you can afford, and move forward with a clear plan.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn--primary btn--hero" href="#waitlist">Join the waitlist</a>
            <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="#showcase">See preview</a>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-note">We’ll email you at App Store launch—nothing else.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-hook" id="hero-hook">The down payment isn’t the whole number. The total cash is.</p>
        <p class="hero-emotional">Buying your first home shouldn’t mean guessing with your biggest savings goal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--insight section--band-muted" id="why-homestart" aria-labelledby="insight-heading">
    <div class="insight-inner">
      <p class="section-label">Why this exists</p>
      <h2 id="insight-heading">Closing, reserves, and move-in money add up—usually before people expect.</h2>
      <p class="insight-tight"><strong>{{ site.name }}</strong> is one number for everything you need at the table—plus savings progress and affordability context before you pick up the phone with a lender.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--preview" id="showcase" aria-labelledby="preview-heading">
    <div class="preview-shell">
      <header class="preview-header">
        <p class="section-label">See the plan in one view</p>
        <h2 id="preview-heading" class="preview-tagline">Your target price, total cash goal, savings gap, and payment estimate—together in one place.</h2>
        <p class="preview-sub">Real iOS screens. Sample data. Final polish underway.</p>
      </header>
      <div class="preview-stage">
        <figure class="app-showcase app-showcase--hero" data-app-preview>
          <div class="mock-frame mock-frame--premium mock-frame--stage">
            <div class="mock-screen mock-screen--photo" role="tabpanel" id="app-preview-panel" aria-labelledby="app-preview-tab-plan">
              <img
                class="app-preview-img"
                src="/images/preview-plan.jpg"
                alt="HomeStart plan overview: target home, closing-cash progress, estimated payment, and savings summary. Sample data."
                width="471"
                height="1024"
                decoding="async"
                fetchpriority="high"
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="preview-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Switch app preview screen">
            <button type="button" class="preview-tab" role="tab" id="app-preview-tab-plan" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="app-preview-panel" data-preview-src="/images/preview-plan.jpg" data-preview-alt="HomeStart plan overview: target home, closing-cash progress, estimated payment, and savings summary. Sample data." data-preview-explain="Plan — your target home, closing-cash progress, and monthly payment context on one screen.">Plan</button>
            <button type="button" class="preview-tab" role="tab" id="app-preview-tab-numbers" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="app-preview-panel" data-preview-src="/images/preview-numbers.jpg" data-preview-alt="HomeStart numbers view: readiness score and savings, cash-to-close, and payment comfort. Sample data." data-preview-explain="Numbers — readiness-style scores for savings pace, cash to close, and how comfortable a future payment looks.">Numbers</button>
            <button type="button" class="preview-tab" role="tab" id="app-preview-tab-accounts" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="app-preview-panel" data-preview-src="/images/preview-accounts.jpg" data-preview-alt="HomeStart accounts view: linked home fund, progress toward goal, and cash breakdown by purpose. Sample data." data-preview-explain="Accounts — linked home fund total, progress toward your cash goal, and savings grouped by purpose (down payment, closing, reserves).">Accounts</button>
          </div>
          <p class="showcase__explain" aria-live="polite">Plan — your target home, closing-cash progress, and monthly payment context on one screen.</p>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--trust section--band-surface" id="trust" aria-labelledby="trust-heading">
    <p class="section-label" id="trust-heading">Built for planning, not pressure</p>
    <ul class="trust-grid" role="list">
      <li class="trust-pill">
        <span class="trust-pill__label">Planning, not lending</span>
        <span class="trust-pill__text">HomeStart helps you prepare. Real loan terms still come from your lender.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="trust-pill">
        <span class="trust-pill__label">Linking is optional</span>
        <span class="trust-pill__text">Use Plaid for live balances, or keep everything manual.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="trust-pill">
        <span class="trust-pill__label">Your data, your choice</span>
        <span class="trust-pill__text">Connect only what you want. <a href="/security-overview/">See how we protect it →</a></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--features section--band-muted" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="section-label">What changes with HomeStart</p>
      <h2 id="features-heading">Clarity before the lender call</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("cash") }}</div>
        <h3>Know the number first</h3>
        <p>Down payment, closing, reserves, and move-in cash—rolled into one clear target.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("savings") }}</div>
        <h3>See your gap close</h3>
        <p>Track savings against your total goal as you move toward buying.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("afford") }}</div>
        <h3>Know what feels affordable</h3>
        <p>Put a future payment next to rent, income, and debts before you commit.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap feature-icon-wrap--accent" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("link") }}</div>
        <h3>Link accounts—or skip it</h3>
        <p>Keep balances updated automatically, or type them in yourself.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card feature-card--wide">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("roadmap") }}</div>
        <h3>Know the next step</h3>
        <p>Short guidance and ordered milestones so progress feels manageable.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cta-mid" aria-labelledby="cta-mid-heading">
    <div class="cta-mid">
      <div class="cta-mid__copy">
        <h2 id="cta-mid-heading">App Store launch is next</h2>
        <p>Join the waitlist and we’ll send the download link when HomeStart is live.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg btn--cta-solid" href="#waitlist">Join the waitlist</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--how section--band-surface" id="how-it-works" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="section-label" id="how-heading">Three steps to a clearer plan</p>
      <h2 class="visually-hidden">How HomeStart works</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h3>Start with your numbers</h3>
        <p>Income, rent, debts, and savings on hand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h3>Set a real target</h3>
        <p>Choose a home price or payment range, then account for taxes, insurance, timing, and cash to close.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h3>Track until you’re ready</h3>
        <p>Update savings, link accounts if you want, and follow the roadmap forward.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--audience section--band-muted" id="audience" aria-labelledby="audience-heading">
    <div class="audience-inner">
      <p class="section-label" id="audience-heading">Built for your first home</p>
      <p class="audience-lead">Not investors. Not flippers. Not another spreadsheet.</p>
      <p class="audience-outro">Just a clearer path to your first set of keys.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--waitlist" id="waitlist" aria-labelledby="waitlist-heading">
    <div class="waitlist waitlist--premium">
      <p class="waitlist__badge">Get the App Store link first</p>
      <h2 id="waitlist-heading">Reserve your spot</h2>
      <p class="waitlist__lead">Join the first wave and we’ll email you when HomeStart launches. Nothing extra.</p>
      <ul class="waitlist__bullets" role="list">
        <li>App Store link at launch</li>
        <li>Occasional milestone notes</li>
        <li>Unsubscribe anytime</li>
      </ul>
      <form class="waitlist-form waitlist-form--premium" id="waitlist-form" novalidate>
        <div class="field-wrap">
          <label class="visually-hidden" for="waitlist-email">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" id="waitlist-email" name="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="you@email.com" required inputmode="email">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--submit btn--lg btn--cta-solid" id="waitlist-submit">Join the waitlist</button>
      </form>
      <p class="waitlist__fineprint">Waitlist and launch only. <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a></p>
      <div class="waitlist-status" id="waitlist-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <span class="footer-brand">{{ site.name }}</span>
    <ul class="footer-links">
      <li><a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy</a></li>
      <li><a href="/terms-of-service/">Terms</a></li>
      <li><a href="/security-overview/">Security</a></li>
      <li><a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="footer-meta">© {{ site.copyrightYear }} {{ site.companyLegalName }}</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  (function () {
    var h = document.getElementById("site-header");
    if (!h) return;
    function tick() {
      h.classList.toggle("is-scrolled", window.scrollY > 8);
    }
    tick();
    window.addEventListener("scroll", tick, { passive: true });
  })();
</script>
